# Global Claude instructions (all projects on this machine)

This is an EXAMPLE file - setup-machine.ps1 skips *.example files.
To use: copy to CLAUDE.md in this folder, put your real global rules in,
commit (in your private fork), and run bootstrap\setup-machine.ps1 on
each new machine.

Typical content: pointers to personal global skills, machine-wide
preferences, private conventions that apply to every project.
